Founded by Private Entrepreneur Ernest Chakhoyan in 2020, book.me is the first reservation
application in Armenia. It was created to reserve seats in your preferred places such as gaming
hubs, cafes, restaurants, hotels, etc. Our main goal is to develop and enlarge app functionality
so that our users can be more flexible in managing their time in nearly all aspects of their lives.
